metadata.description:
57 may or may not be notable.

1st of 5 tokens scheduled for mint in SB Checks Collection.

‘57’ is the base for an interactive OE burn series centered around The Big Game. You will need to burn 2 '57's in order to choose a side for Sunday. Picking the right side will qualify you for our SB NFT Giveaway to be held after the game concludes. Choose wisely, anon.

By owning all 5 tokens at the conclusion of the burn series, you will qualify for our final airdrop.  
At minimum to complete the set without secondary, you will need to mint 9 ‘57’s.

Snapshots will be taken as needed to facilitate the series and maintain integrity.
